<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 12:12:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>联合国最高法院开始就以色列占领巴勒斯坦领土举行听证会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/top-un-court-begins-hearings-into-israels-occupation-of-palestinian-territories/0000018d-c0c4-df10-a99f-d7f7f67e0000</link><description>国际法院开始就以色列占领约旦河西岸、加沙和东耶路撒冷问题举行为期六天的听证会，前所未有的 51 个国家将在听证会上发言</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/top-un-court-begins-hearings-into-israels-occupation-of-palestinian-territories/0000018d-c0c4-df10-a99f-d7f7f67e0000</guid></item><item><title>两项可能推翻内塔尼亚胡政府的法律草案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/two-draft-laws-that-could-bring-down-netanyahus-government/0000018d-c019-dfd7-a9fd-f39d96c60000</link><description>两项极不受欢迎的军事征兵法涉及以色列境内深刻的政治、安全和社会紧张局势，很可能成为内塔尼亚胡政府垮台的基石 — — 并将影响加沙战争的继续</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:26:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/two-draft-laws-that-could-bring-down-netanyahus-government/0000018d-c019-dfd7-a9fd-f39d96c60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列伞兵在加沙地带南部的战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/israeli-paratrooper-killed-in-combat-in-southern-gaza-strip/0000018d-c095-df10-a99f-d7f7afcb0000</link><description>参谋军士。西蒙·什洛莫夫（Simon Shlomov）于2021年从哈萨克斯坦移民到以色列，当时是以色列陆军伞兵旅的一名孤独士兵</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:08:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/israeli-paratrooper-killed-in-combat-in-southern-gaza-strip/0000018d-c095-df10-a99f-d7f7afcb0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔的助手向同事、媒体人员和议员的妻子发放持枪许可证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-aides-hand-out-gun-permits-to-associates-media-personnel-and-lawmakers-wife/0000018d-c05f-dfd7-a9fd-f3dfea4b0000</link><description>在其平台上赞扬极右翼部长本-格维尔的媒体人士提交的许可证申请疑似在快速审批过程中获得批准，其中一些申请不符合标准</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-aides-hand-out-gun-permits-to-associates-media-personnel-and-lawmakers-wife/0000018d-c05f-dfd7-a9fd-f3dfea4b0000</guid></item><item><title>虽然以色列避免讨论加沙战争“第二天”，但巴勒斯坦人正在制定一项计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/while-israel-avoids-discussing-the-day-after-the-palestinians-are-working-on-a-plan/0000018d-c05d-dc8c-a3df-f27de4800000</link><description>由于担心其政治前途，哈马斯可能被迫加入巴解组织并承认其在加沙地带的地位。华盛顿、相关阿拉伯国家和巴勒斯坦组织目前正竞相为加沙的未来制定切合实际的工作计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 09:45:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/while-israel-avoids-discussing-the-day-after-the-palestinians-are-working-on-a-plan/0000018d-c05d-dc8c-a3df-f27de4800000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在美国压力下抵制国际社会承认巴勒斯坦国的呼吁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-fighting-intl-call-to-recognize-palestinian-state-under-u-s-pressure/0000018d-bdee-dc8c-a3df-ffff03880000</link><description>以色列总理内塔尼亚胡发起了反对单方面承认巴勒斯坦国的运动，称各方之间的直接谈判是建立巴勒斯坦国的唯一途径。虽然这是以色列全面采取的一项受欢迎的举措，但它可能无助于阻止国际认可</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 03:50:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-fighting-intl-call-to-recognize-palestinian-state-under-u-s-pressure/0000018d-bdee-dc8c-a3df-ffff03880000</guid></item><item><title>议会将就因签署国际法院请愿书而驱逐 MK Ofer Cassif 进行投票</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/knesset-to-vote-on-expulsion-of-mk-ofer-cassif-over-signing-icj-petition/0000018d-bdec-dc8c-a3df-fffdab8b0000</link><description>此次驱逐投票是由于哈达什党议员在国际法院支持南非种族灭绝案件而引发的。此举需要议会120名议员中90名的批准。截至目前，76名议员计划支持开除卡西夫，20名尚未回应，24名反对</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 03:39:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/knesset-to-vote-on-expulsion-of-mk-ofer-cassif-over-signing-icj-petition/0000018d-bdec-dc8c-a3df-fffdab8b0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔外交部称内塔尼亚胡的言论“试图阻止和延长”加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article-live/pm-sides-with-far-right-to-limit-arab-israeli-visits-to-al-aqsa-during-ramadan/0000018d-bee3-dc8c-a3df-fef730a70000</link><description>联合国最高法院开始就以色列控制巴勒斯坦领土问题举行听证会 ■ 以色列国防军表示正在深化在汗尤尼斯的行动 ■ 哈马斯称其 6,000 名武装分子被杀，一半以色列声称拥有主权 ■ 也门胡塞武装称他们在红海击落船只并击落美国无人机</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 01:19:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article-live/pm-sides-with-far-right-to-limit-arab-israeli-visits-to-al-aqsa-during-ramadan/0000018d-bee3-dc8c-a3df-fef730a70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列关于斋月祈祷的决定是一场闹剧。可能会以悲剧告终</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-decision-on-ramadan-prayers-is-a-farce-it-could-end-in-tragedy/0000018d-be17-df10-a99f-bff71f5b0000</link><description>本·格维尔试图对阿克萨清真寺的阿拉伯裔以色列信徒实行全面限制，但并未完全成功。但这并没有阻止他幸灾乐祸——并冒着引发宗教冲突的风险</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 22:04:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-decision-on-ramadan-prayers-is-a-farce-it-could-end-in-tragedy/0000018d-be17-df10-a99f-bff71f5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院驳回加沙被拘留者寻求法律代表的请求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-denies-petition-for-gaza-detainees-to-access-legal-representation/0000018d-be00-dd5e-a59d-ffb294300000</link><description>战争期间被拘留并被关押在以色列的 62 名加沙居民的家人要求提供有关他们及其拘留地点的信息。大法官以技术理由驳回请愿书，理由是请愿书涉及不同的案件，妨碍了清晰度</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 21:48:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-denies-petition-for-gaza-detainees-to-access-legal-representation/0000018d-be00-dd5e-a59d-ffb294300000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡支持极右翼要求，要求在斋月期间限制阿克萨清真寺的阿拉伯以色列信徒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-backs-far-right-demand-to-limit-arab-israeli-worshipers-at-al-aqsa-in-ramadan/0000018d-bd60-dc8c-a3df-ff75cc820000</link><description>信徒的年龄限制和居住区域将在即将进行的审议中确定，可能会根据警方的立场而定。安全官员警告总理不要阻止巴勒斯坦穆斯林进入阿克萨清真寺</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 20:27:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-backs-far-right-demand-to-limit-arab-israeli-worshipers-at-al-aqsa-in-ramadan/0000018d-bd60-dc8c-a3df-ff75cc820000</guid></item><item><title>拉马拉呼吁美国支持巴勒斯坦权力机构成为联合国会员国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/ramallah-calls-on-u-s-to-back-palestinian-authority-as-un-member-state/0000018d-bda8-dc8c-a3df-ffbd776d0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦权力机构的一名高级官员告诉《国土报》，国际社会在宣布两国解决方案的同时，还应该采取行动来证明其严肃性。巴勒斯坦权力机构总理表示，只要哈马斯接受“先决条件”，它准备与哈马斯合作</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 19:54:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/ramallah-calls-on-u-s-to-back-palestinian-authority-as-un-member-state/0000018d-bda8-dc8c-a3df-ffbd776d0000</guid></item><item><title>讲述以色列从第二次起义到有史以来最严重的加沙战争的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/telling-israels-story-from-the-second-intifada-to-its-worst-ever-gaza-war/0000018d-bc61-dd5e-a59d-fdf3f1d80000</link><description>以色列年度当地见证展览的最佳照片已汇集在一本书中。展览创始人 Dana Wohlfeiler-Lalkin 带我们经历个人和国家之旅</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 18:50:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/telling-israels-story-from-the-second-intifada-to-its-worst-ever-gaza-war/0000018d-bc61-dd5e-a59d-fdf3f1d80000</guid></item><item><title>历史性胜利：以色列游泳运动员在多哈世锦赛上获得银牌，遭到嘘声</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-swimmer-takes-silver-medal-booed-at-doha-world-championships/0000018d-bd78-dd5e-a59d-fdfa980b0000</link><description>“我很高兴来到这里，”阿纳斯塔西娅·戈尔本科说道，尽管卡塔尔首都的当地观众发出了嘘声。周日，她成为第一位在同一届世锦赛上两次闯入个人决赛的以色列人，在预赛中获得第五名</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 18:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-swimmer-takes-silver-medal-booed-at-doha-world-championships/0000018d-bd78-dd5e-a59d-fdfa980b0000</guid></item><item><title>煤气灯操纵者头目内塔尼亚胡鼓吹“团结”，播下分裂种子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-18/ty-article/.highlight/gaslighter-in-chief-netanyahu-sows-division-by-preaching-unity/0000018d-bd2c-df10-a99f-bfff7a970000</link><description>对内塔尼亚胡的批评来自勇敢的赎罪日战争老兵，这一事实对他来说似乎并不重要，就像来自加沙被扣押人质家属的批评一样。当谈到为他的政治生存而战时，所有对手都是公平的游戏</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 18:31:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-18/ty-article/.highlight/gaslighter-in-chief-netanyahu-sows-division-by-preaching-unity/0000018d-bd2c-df10-a99f-bfff7a970000</guid></item><item><title>以色列边境警察在约旦河西岸受重伤，两名巴勒斯坦人丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-border-police-officer-seriously-wounded-in-west-bank-two-palestinians-killed/0000018d-bd04-df10-a99f-bff742310000</link><description>据以色列国防军称，以色列军队进入约旦河西岸图尔卡姆难民营，逮捕一名参与恐怖袭击并涉嫌谋杀据称与以色列勾结的巴勒斯坦人的通缉犯。</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 18:28:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-border-police-officer-seriously-wounded-in-west-bank-two-palestinians-killed/0000018d-bd04-df10-a99f-bff742310000</guid></item><item><title>新民意调查发现，以色列公众将“击败哈马斯”置于确保人质返回之上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/survey-israeli-public-prioritizes-defeating-hamas-over-ensuring-hostages-return/0000018d-bd09-df10-a99f-bffbdf580000</link><description>除其他外，调查发现，自战争开始以来，公众对以色列赢得战争能力的信心，包括对以色列国防军指挥梯队的信任，已经受到削弱，而对该国政治领导层的信任达到了历史最高水平。低的</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 18:10:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/survey-israeli-public-prioritizes-defeating-hamas-over-ensuring-hostages-return/0000018d-bd09-df10-a99f-bffbdf580000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 135 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-135/0000018d-bd37-dc8c-a3df-ff37f8020000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡政府一致通过决议，拒绝国际单方面承认巴勒斯坦国 ■ 甘茨：如果斋月期间不释放哈马斯扣押的人质，以色列将扩大对拉法的地面行动 ■ 欧盟消息人士称，他们帮助将原本为以色列人质提供的药品带入加沙 ■ 巴西卢拉总统将以色列在加沙的行动与大屠杀进行比较 ■ 这是战争 135 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 17:30:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-135/0000018d-bd37-dc8c-a3df-ff37f8020000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院应联合国要求考虑以色列控制西岸和东耶路撒冷的合法性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/icj-to-consider-legality-of-israels-control-over-west-bank-and-east-jerusalem/0000018d-bcd4-dd5e-a59d-fdf6fb5a0000</link><description>联合国大会要求海牙联合国最高法院就这一问题提供不具约束力的法律意见，但预计许多国家将予以高度重视</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 16:37:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/icj-to-consider-legality-of-israels-control-over-west-bank-and-east-jerusalem/0000018d-bcd4-dd5e-a59d-fdf6fb5a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡抨击巴西总统卢拉将以色列在加沙的行动与“希特勒的种族灭绝”相比较</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/netanyahu-slams-brazils-lula-for-comparing-israels-gaza-actions-to-hitlers-genocide/0000018d-bcaa-df10-a99f-bffb0da90000</link><description>巴西总统说：“加沙地带和巴勒斯坦人民所发生的事情在任何其他历史时刻都不存在。”事实上，当希特勒决定屠杀犹太人时，它就已经存在了。以色列宣布将传唤巴西大使进行谴责</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 16:02:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/netanyahu-slams-brazils-lula-for-comparing-israels-gaza-actions-to-hitlers-genocide/0000018d-bcaa-df10-a99f-bffb0da90000</guid></item></channel></rss>